				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%C3%A1t-ai-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-7-C%E1%BB%91-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-t%C3%A1c-lang-bi%E1%BA%BFm-Thai-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%99-Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-c%C3%B4ng-Ki%E1%BB%81n/poem-7W9_oz5KbHyRecrZub-UXQ">Bát ai thi kỳ 7 - Cố trước tác lang biếm Thai Châu tư hộ Huỳnh Dương Trịnh công Kiền - 八哀詩其七－故著作郎貶台州司戶滎陽鄭公虔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-08/poem-mx69qCtYu2R3IzHCgoufZA">Cảm ngộ kỳ 08 - 感遇其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/D%C3%A3-v%E1%BB%8Dng-N%E1%BA%A1p-n%E1%BA%A1p-c%C3%A0n-kh%C3%B4n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i/poem-IKc7EODoeBqyyW7VYjZl5Q">Dã vọng (Nạp nạp càn khôn đại) - 野望（納納乾坤大）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/D%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-tr%C3%BAc-k%C3%BD/poem-USjIEvm0BXvGANiMbyuxOg">Dưỡng trúc ký - 養竹記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-%C3%94ng-M%E1%BA%B7c-%C4%90%C3%A0m-thi%E1%BA%BFu-b%E1%BA%A3o-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Ngh%C4%A9a-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-WXaXT7cJsCVepWZ86f_QxQ">Đề Ông Mặc Đàm thiếu bảo Tiết Nghĩa từ - 題翁墨譚少保節義祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/author-7tg_rhleFYVL5Ann2EB2iA">Trần Danh Án</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/%C4%90i%E1%BA%BFu-ng%C3%A3-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-MSop8fUz6YY5qcic9LGajg">Điếu ngã tử - 吊餓死</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Qu%C3%A1-Nam-nh%E1%BA%A1c-nh%E1%BA%ADp-%C4%90%E1%BB%99ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-h%E1%BB%93/poem-9myXxdyuGsX0zxdHRnQwXQ">Quá Nam nhạc nhập Động Đình hồ - 過南嶽入洞庭湖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Th%E1%BB%B1c-%C4%90%C3%ACnh/poem--ppSF8KhTOlbANcnV7XUYg">Tặng Thực Đình - 贈實亭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-Ng%C3%B4-th%E1%BA%A5t-du-Th%E1%BB%A5c/poem-q0qzQDHH0yeSGBUuH4q3MA">Tống Ngô thất du Thục - 送吳七遊蜀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-jvbfrjspi2Y6S8b3jeqzpA">Lạc Tân Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/V%C3%A3n-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Vi/poem-O-mzzJipLHpu9vq59HkvjQ">Vãn Trần Trọng Vi - 輓陳仲微</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-wmykBdQiZlhullR0PPvO_Q">Trần Thánh Tông</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
